        "description": "Commercial CFD solver (ANSYS Fluent 2023 R2) must hold a 21 CFR Part 11-compliant validation certificate; in-house UDF hemolysis model must be version-controlled in a validated repository with traceability to test reports; regression test suite must cover all hemolysis-relevant code paths with ≥95% branch coverage."
      },
      "rationale": "ANSYS Fluent 2023 R2 holds a current FDA 21 CFR Part 11 software validation certificate (SVC-2023-FL-0047). In-house hemolysis UDF v2.4.1 is stored in a Git repository with signed commits; regression suite (87 unit tests, 12 integration tests) achieves 96% branch coverage. Independent SQA audit completed 2024-01-15 with no critical findings."
