      },
      "rationale": "MMS verification on Navier-Stokes solver confirms second-order spatial accuracy (observed order 1.94 ± 0.06) and first-order temporal accuracy for steady RANS. Two ASME V&V 20 benchmark cases (lid-driven cavity Re=1000, backward-facing step Re=800) reproduced within 1.2% and 2.7% of reference solutions respectively. Hemolysis scalar transport UDF verified via analytical solution for constant-shear Couette flow."
