      "rationale": "NIH predictions compared against bench measurements at five operating points. Maximum percent error = 17.3% (OP-3, 4 L/min, 3500 RPM). All five predictions below clinical threshold; Monte Carlo 95th-percentile bound also below threshold. RMSE across all points = 0.00062 g/100 L. Velocity field RMSE < 0.08 m/s; all within experimental uncertainty envelope per ASME V&V 20 validation metric."
