      },
      "rationale": "Simulation Execution Procedure SEP-COU2-v2.1 followed for all runs; signed off by lead analyst (PE, 12 years CFD experience). Independent peer review conducted by second qualified analyst (DR-2024-COU2); no critical findings. Post-processing Python scripts version-controlled and independently validated against manual spot-checks at OP-1 and OP-5. Training records for both analysts current as of 2024-03-01."
