      "rationale": "Fluid properties (viscosity, density) sourced from ISO 10993-4 Annex B with ±3% uncertainty. Hemolysis correlation coefficients (α=3.62×10⁻⁵, β=2.416, γ=0.785) from Giersiepen et al. 1990 with ±15% coefficient uncertainty per Arora et al. 2004. Boundary conditions derived from direct measurement (PIV, Coriolis flow meter). All 14 uncertain inputs propagated through 5000-sample Latin Hypercube Monte Carlo ensemble; input sensitivity indices (Sobol first-order) computed and archived."
